The USA has tried to be peaceable with terrorists for decades now.  Hell, Bin Laden bombed US embassies in Africa not so long ago but we held back.  The USA has been exemplary in its dealings with terrorists.  We have tried to seek peaceful solutions, peace talks that worked for what? A day and a half?  Because the USA is the most powerful nation on the earth, we have taken that as a responsibility and have not acted like bullies.  Yet the “Chihuahuas” continued to “yipe” and bite at our heals.  Terrorist continued to bomb innocents all over the world.  Innocents have died by the hundreds to terrorist activities, laughing at the fact that they keep getting away with it.<br>
